Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================OP============================
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.14,0:01:29.51,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}找不到合适的话语　轻抚你的肩头
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.59,0:01:36.14,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}你一言不发　冷冷挣脱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.21,0:01:42.68,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}小小的误解　令年轻的爱瓦解
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.79,0:01:49.78,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}不想见你悲伤的脸庞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.21,0:01:56.47,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}即便抛弃梦想　请别抛弃你的微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.86,0:02:02.79,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}让它永远在我心中闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.49,0:02:07.73,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}有一天　不同的你我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.78,0:02:10.90,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}携手筑起未来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.02,0:02:17.66,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}回到曾经的地方　不论身在何方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.74,0:02:24.56,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}现在二人只有悲伤地错开视线
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.97,0:02:29.70,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}相信后会有期
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================ED============================
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.29,0:22:06.12,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(500,500)\an3}心与心邂逅　呼唤遥远真实
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.29,0:22:17.42,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(500,2500)\an3}逆涛卷浪相隔　呼喊同一个梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.46,0:22:30.36,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(500,500)}不堪回首　互相争斗的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.66,0:22:38.54,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(500,500)}轻抚脸颊　微微一笑释之
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.72,0:22:46.67,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(500,500)}驻足于此　不见星之歌声
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.80,0:22:56.84,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(500,500)}奏出名为爱的幻曲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.88,0:23:04.56,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(500,500)}心与心远离　呼唤遥远真实
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.90,0:23:16.17,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(500,500)}天边卷云翻滚　眺望同一缕光明
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================Avant============================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.18,0:00:03.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡嘉莉想打仗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.17,0:00:07.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想让战争结束！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.12,0:00:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 打是打不完的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.48,0:00:12.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争这东西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.95,0:00:14.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.35,0:00:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同情？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.01,0:00:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 同情我？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.82,0:00:21.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.81,0:00:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.59,0:00:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,错了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.14,0:00:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.50,0:00:32.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.33,0:00:36.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论遇到什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.58,0:00:40.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们都不会把真相告诉他
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.85,0:00:44.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括兄妹的事…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.57,0:00:48.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你…的？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.84,0:00:52.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.70,0:00:57.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是朋友送给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.68,0:01:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宝贵的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.62,0:01:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================Main============================
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.32,0:02:42.83,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1184,576)}{\fad(500,500)}{\bord3\shad1\be20\an3\fs60}命运之杵
Dialogue: 1,0:02:38.32,0:02:42.83,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1184,576)}{\fad(500,500)}{\bord2\shad0\1a&HFF&\3a&H00&\an3\fs60}命运之杵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.71,0:02:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前最大的不安因素是巴拿马
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.83,0:02:46.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据传扎夫特有大规模作战行动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.25,0:02:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡本塔里亚最近非常活跃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.78,0:02:52.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们了解多少
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.19,0:02:54.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.61,0:02:56.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥布的处境也很微妙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.83,0:02:59.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想得到情报 但又不想摊上麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.66,0:03:05.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 这样对你们回到阿拉斯加反而有利吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.43,0:03:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万一遇到追击
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.93,0:03:09.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要越过北回归线
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.33,0:03:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不远就是阿拉斯加的防空圈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.96,0:03:14.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们不会傻到继续追击吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.30,0:03:17.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那支对我们紧追不舍的部队动向如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.46,0:03:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前天开始 就没有在奥布近海发现舰艇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.84,0:03:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤走了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.74,0:03:27.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外交渠道上一定发生了许多事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.77,0:03:29.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望是那样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.18,0:03:34.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传闻阿斯哈前代表当时
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.44,0:03:37.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对这艘船和机动战士的建造并不知情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.66,0:03:39.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.50,0:03:41.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴基露露中尉！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.99,0:03:46.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实 前代表并不知情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.54,0:03:50.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部分官僚迫于大西洋联邦压力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.08,0:03:51.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自作主张进行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.34,0:03:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并暗地与曙光社勾结
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.43,0:03:57.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人认为奥布应该明确立场
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.86,0:04:00.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这想法没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.54,0:04:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但一旦那样 到时遭殃的是国民
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.24,0:04:05.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像赫利奥波利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.64,0:04:09.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为避免那种情况
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.38,0:04:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌兹米大人明知艰难
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.30,0:04:12.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍顶住压力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.17,0:04:17.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许在你们看来 这样有些天真
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.25,0:04:19.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.14,0:04:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修理进展如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.86,0:04:24.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说明天内完成
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.83,0:04:27.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就快了 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.64,0:04:34.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城坂一校
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.05,0:04:39.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢你的协助
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.61,0:04:42.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 你们帮了我大忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.82,0:04:44.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在是光棍一条
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.47,0:04:46.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在塔西莱长大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.64,0:04:50.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明知暂时的胜利没有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.18,0:04:53.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不能视而不见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.29,0:05:00.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少安全带回了顽皮的离家少女
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.91,0:05:02.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才应该感谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.17,0:05:14.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不懂 他打算干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.98,0:05:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是 还接受了补给
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.07,0:05:25.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长腿在奥布 不会错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.81,0:05:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们出来就会北上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.80,0:05:29.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里撒网
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.78,0:05:31.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？给我等下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.26,0:05:34.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你凭什么这么肯定？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.14,0:05:37.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先回卡本塔里亚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.19,0:05:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重新梳理一下情报会不会比较好？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.61,0:05:42.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果…没有明确证据的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.10,0:05:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 他们在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.85,0:05:48.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经在这里泡了2天！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.61,0:05:52.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万一错了长腿已经远在天边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.45,0:05:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想造反我可以帮忙哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.76,0:05:57.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 来场哗变？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.58,0:06:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.76,0:06:05.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还没单纯到这种地步
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.68,0:06:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前的朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.46,0:06:25.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是朋友送给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.41,0:06:28.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宝贵的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.55,0:06:31.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你在铁丝网的另一边
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.04,0:06:36.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是 当时袭击赫利奥波利斯的一员吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.10,0:06:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道奥布不该造它
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.02,0:06:41.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是它…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.36,0:06:42.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那架机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.71,0:06:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还会杀好多地球上的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.38,0:06:48.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡嘉莉·尤拉·阿斯哈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.16,0:06:51.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实不是地球军…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.57,0:06:54.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.10,0:06:59.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,补给完成了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.32,0:07:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.52,0:07:03.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对面甲板上能看到飞鱼群
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.99,0:07:05.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去看看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.50,0:07:06.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.39,0:07:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不安…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.14,0:07:11.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.86,0:07:13.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.42,0:07:15.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信阿斯兰…不
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.27,0:07:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信队长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.11,0:07:24.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼科尔怎么会想到参军的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.02,0:07:25.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.65,0:07:28.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.63,0:07:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我多管闲事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.71,0:07:31.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.14,0:07:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉自己也应该出一份力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.13,0:07:39.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到尤尼乌斯7号的新闻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.12,0:07:42.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.57,0:07:46.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和尼科尔一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.49,0:07:51.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始注水
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.04,0:07:53.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始注水
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.58,0:07:54.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始注水
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.99,0:08:12.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.60,0:08:14.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,模拟训练已经滚瓜烂熟了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.59,0:08:15.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.24,0:08:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两架能一起出击确实好处不少
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.36,0:08:22.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强袭在地球上吃亏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.37,0:08:23.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是多尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.06,0:08:27.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支援和上空监视而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.06,0:08:29.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴基露露中尉命令你的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.36,0:08:31.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我志愿的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.97,0:08:33.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也得出份力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.93,0:08:57.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停车
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.77,0:09:00.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.63,0:09:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡嘉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.48,0:09:13.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算和那艘船一起走？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.01,0:09:14.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.11,0:09:19.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 作为地球军的士兵和PLANT作战？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.22,0:09:21.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就这么喜欢战斗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.31,0:09:23.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.49,0:09:24.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是想打仗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.59,0:09:27.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.51,0:09:29.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想帮他们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.36,0:09:31.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 想尽早结束
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.20,0:09:32.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的战争
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.28,0:09:35.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去就能结束战争吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.95,0:09:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 打是打不完的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.12,0:09:41.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争这东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.23,0:09:44.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么怎么分出胜负？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.62,0:09:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到把敌人 全部消灭光
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.15,0:09:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.57,0:09:52.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.42,0:09:56.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你每射杀一个父亲 就会有一个妻子恨你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.12,0:10:01.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你每射杀一个儿子 就会有一个母亲恨你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.53,0:10:04.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你若死于谁的枪下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.10,0:10:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会对他恨之入骨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.03,0:10:10.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么简单的道理为什么不懂？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.68,0:10:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.27,0:10:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 自己在这个和平的国家…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.03,0:10:19.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种肤浅的、自我满足的正义感能做成什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.23,0:10:24.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并非只有拿起枪来才是战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.18,0:10:27.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学习战争的本质 卡嘉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.76,0:10:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.48,0:10:32.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,互相射击不会带来任何解决
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.12,0:10:40.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥布军通知
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.86,0:10:42.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周边没有舰影
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.64,0:10:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请按时出发
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.52,0:10:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉他们明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.51,0:10:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要出动护卫舰吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.60,0:10:50.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了掩人耳目
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.08,0:10:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多几艘不容易被识别
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.81,0:10:56.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数据事后可以任意修改
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.63,0:11:08.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯哈前代表来到船坞送行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.74,0:11:12.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们要求大和少尉上甲板
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.67,0:11:18.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.73,0:11:22.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡嘉莉 怎么会？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.82,0:11:26.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的父母 在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.27,0:11:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 为什么不肯见他们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.42,0:11:48.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.28,0:11:52.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.46,0:11:55.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 替我转告好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.98,0:11:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在…我不能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.47,0:12:08.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.97,0:12:12.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡嘉莉也保重
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.05,0:12:15.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 非常感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.75,0:12:17.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.40,0:12:25.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可别死哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.78,0:12:30.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 我已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.06,0:13:34.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是演习吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.49,0:13:36.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日程表上没有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.42,0:13:37.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝东北方向
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.12,0:13:39.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认舰体 还没完成吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.88,0:13:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进入战斗准备
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.77,0:13:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请抓紧确认
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.89,0:13:48.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即将离开领海
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.55,0:13:49.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周边没有敌影
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.12,0:13:51.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,严密戒备
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.63,0:13:54.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脱离舰队后升空 最大战速
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.75,0:13:56.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰队旗舰来电
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.60,0:14:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我部就此返航 祝贵舰好运
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.11,0:14:03.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回复他们感谢护航
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.97,0:14:05.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 孩子这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.02,0:14:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没下任何命令呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.94,0:14:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离开领海以后
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.08,0:14:12.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扎夫特就会开始攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.05,0:14:34.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌舰队有舰船离开队列
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.32,0:14:36.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰种确认 是长腿！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.79,0:14:40.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜中了 阿斯兰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.11,0:14:44.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出击 今天一定要击落长腿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.34,0:14:46.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认上浮完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.21,0:14:48.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开舱门
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.76,0:14:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路线清空
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.83,0:14:52.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始弹射
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.21,0:15:08.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷达反应
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.58,0:15:10.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数量3 不…4！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.06,0:15:15.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认机种 神盾 暴风 迅雷 决斗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.47,0:15:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏在附近 撒网等我们来？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.62,0:15:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反潜 反机动战士 战斗准备
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.45,0:15:28.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要摆脱就好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.91,0:15:31.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会是一场硬仗 大家倾尽全力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.34,0:15:33.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ECM最大强度
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.35,0:15:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烟雾榴弹发射器发射
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.16,0:15:36.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两舷放烟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.09,0:15:42.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连接电源
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.39,0:15:43.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辅助能量上线
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.97,0:15:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成待命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.95,0:16:04.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.69,0:16:06.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从上空给强袭支援就行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.49,0:16:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.38,0:16:10.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走 被给打中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.66,0:16:16.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路线清空 空中霸王凯尼机出击
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.09,0:16:18.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千万小心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.58,0:16:24.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烟雾？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.76,0:16:26.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 耍小聪明
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.00,0:16:28.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两架？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.81,0:16:35.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 不错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.89,0:16:37.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支援强袭 就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.37,0:16:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.20,0:16:41.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是空中霸王凯尼机
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.07,0:16:43.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强袭 听得见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.47,0:16:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就传送敌人坐标和射击数据
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.41,0:16:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.12,0:16:49.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.56,0:16:56.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散开
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.95,0:17:09.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强袭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.46,0:17:12.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往前禁止通行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.51,0:17:22.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.28,0:17:30.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊扎克 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.41,0:17:34.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.98,0:17:51.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柏瑞安 发射
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.81,0:18:04.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢量数据连接航行计算机
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.29,0:18:07.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺曼少尉 保持方向舵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.32,0:18:08.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.89,0:18:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗拉戈机到位
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.63,0:18:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强袭 请准备换装空袭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.67,0:18:17.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接好礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.25,0:18:19.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校 请
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.29,0:18:38.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙 在空中换装？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.37,0:18:41.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.79,0:18:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.80,0:19:07.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.30,0:19:12.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.39,0:19:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.27,0:19:15.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多尔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.21,0:19:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.26,0:19:30.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.10,0:19:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.32,0:20:06.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉 发射剑袭了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.42,0:20:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多尔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.59,0:20:16.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.85,0:20:18.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.39,0:20:24.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停止射击
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.77,0:20:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大和上尉 不要深追
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.12,0:20:31.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快撤退 你们输了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.92,0:20:32.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.74,0:20:36.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 阿斯兰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.50,0:20:38.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想继续和你打
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.47,0:20:44.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.90,0:20:46.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开枪就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.30,0:20:48.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你当时也说过
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.66,0:20:53.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也说过 会向我开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.80,0:21:12.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.12,0:21:15.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰让开
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.51,0:21:43.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰 逃…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.66,0:21:46.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次也要平安
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.65,0:21:51.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 我的钢琴…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.37,0:22:12.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼科尔！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================Next============================
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.17,0:23:25.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失在爆尘中的温柔脸庞
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.70,0:23:27.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的梦想 未来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.27,0:23:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后悔已无法挽回
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.29,0:23:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这令人难以接受的现实
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.85,0:23:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拷问着阿斯兰的心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.39,0:23:36.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是命运吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.96,0:23:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战场相遇就是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.25,0:23:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再次见面的基拉和阿斯兰
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.47,0:23:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二人死斗的最后…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.09,0:23:46.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 机动战士高达SEED
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.53,0:23:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「闪光之刻」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.37,0:23:50.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿越在业火中吧 高达
